px;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;color:#333333">如何用案例管理法解决问题</span></p><p style="margin-left:91px;line-height:150%"><span style="font-size:16px;line-height:150%;font-family:Wingdings;color:#333333">l<span style="font:9px &#39;Times New Roman&#39;">&nbsp; </span></span><span style="font-size:16px;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;color:#333333">如何用案管理法规避管理风险</span></p><p style="margin-left:63px;line-height:150%"><span style="font-size:16px;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;color:#333333">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="line-height:150%"><strong><span style="font-size:16px;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;color:#333333">&nbsp; </span></strong><strong><span style="font-size:16px;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;color:#333333">第五部分：班组管理平台与管理工具</span></strong></p><p style="margin-left:91px;line-height:150%"><span style="font-size:16px;line-height:150%;font-family:Wingdings;color:#333333">l<span style="font:9px &#39;Times New Roman&#39;">&nbsp; </span></span><span style="font-size:16px;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;color:#333333">班组七大管理机制建设与工具应用</span></p><p style="margin-left:91px;line-height:150%"><span style="font-size:16px;line-height:150%;font-family:Wingdings;color:#333333">l<span style="font:9px &#39;Times New Roman&#39;">&nbsp; </span></span><span style="font-size:16px;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;color:#333333">班组日常化管理平台建设与实践</span></p><p style="margin-left:91px;line-height:150%"><span style="font-size:16px;line-height:150%;font-family:Wingdings;color:#333333">l<span style="font:9px &#39;Times New Roman&#39;">&nbsp; </span></span><span style="font-size:16px;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;color:#333333">班组透明化管理平台建设与实践</span></p><p style="margin-left:91px;line-height:150%"><span style="font-size:16px;line-height:150%;font-family:Wingdings;color:#333333">l<span style="font:9px &#39;Times New Roman&#39;">&nbsp; </span></span><span style="font-size:16px;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;color:#333333">班组改善计划制定与推进</span></p><p><br/></p>', 1374989430, 1);
INSERT INTO `np_courses` (`id`, `type`, `name`, `photo`, `professor`, `content`, `add_time`, `index`) VALUES
(6, '管理能力提升', '《快速提升领导力与执行力的八个引擎》', '/upload/20130815/13765424208358.jpg', '辰辉', '<p style="margin-left:28px;line-height:150%"><span style="font-family:Wingdings">q<span style="font:9px &#39;Times New Roman&#39;">&nbsp;</span></span><strong><span style=";line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;color:#4D4D4D">培训对象：</span></strong><span style=";line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;color:#4D4D4D">企业各级管理者</span></p><p><strong><span style="font-size:7px;font-family:宋体">&nbsp;</span></strong></p><p style="margin-left:28px;line-height:150%"><span style=";line-height:150%;font-family:Wingdings;color:#4D4D4D">q<span style="font:9px &#39;Times New Roman&#39;">&nbsp; </span></span><strong><span style=";line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;color:#4D4D4D">培训背景：当前很多企业存在如下管理困境</span></strong></p><p style="margin-left:56px;line-height:150%"><span style="font-family:Wingdings;color:#4D4D4D">u<span style="font:9px &#39;Times New Roman&#39;">&nbsp;</span></span><span style="font-family:宋体;color:#4D4D4D">设置了标准和规范，却不能保证员工严格的执行</span></p><p style="margin-left:56px;line-height:150%"><span style="font-family:Wingdings;color:#4D4D4D">u<span style="font:9px &#39;Times New Roman&#39;">&nbsp;</span></span><span style="font-family:宋体;color:#4D4D4D">制订了考核和奖惩，却调动不了员工的积极性</span></p><p style="margin-left:56px;line-height:150%"><span style="font-family:Wingdings;color:#4D4D4D">u<span style="font:9px &#39;Times New Roman&#39;">&nbsp;</span></span><span style="font-family:宋体;color:#4D4D4D">员工各有各的小九九，团队总是无法同心同德</span></p><p style="margin-left:56px;line-height:150%"><span style="font-family:Wingdings;color:#4D4D4D">u<span style="font:9px &#39;Times New Roman&#39;">&nbsp;</span></span><span style="font-family:宋体;color:#4D4D4D">管的松了人浮于事，管的严了阴奉阳违</span></p><p style="margin-left:56px;line-height:150%"><span style="font-family:Wingdings;color:#4D4D4D">u<span style="font:9px &#39;Times New Roman&#39;">&nbsp;</span></span><span style="font-family:宋体;color:#4D4D4D">团队执行力和团队绩效陷入瓶颈，无法进一步获得突破！</span></p><p><span style="font-size:7px;font-family:宋体;color:#4D4D4D">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="margin-left:28px;line-height:150%"><span style=";line-height:150%;font-family:Wingdings;color:#4D4D4D">q<span style="font:9px &#39;Times New Roman&#39;">&nbsp; </span></span><strong><span style=";line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;color:#4D4D4D">课程收益：</span></strong><span style=";line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;color:#4D4D4D">帮助企业各级管理者</span></p><p style="margin-left:56px;line-height:150%"><span style=";line-height:150%;font-family:Wingdings;color:#4D4D4D">u<span style="font:9px &#39;Times New Roman&#39;">&nbsp; </span></span><span style=";line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;color:#4D4D4D">了解团队执行力和绩效差的根本原因</span></p><p style="margin-left:56px;line-height:150%"><span style=";line-height:150%;font-family:Wingdings;color:#4D4D4D">u<span style="font:9px &#39;Times New Roman&#39;">&nbsp; </span></span><span style=";line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;color:#4D4D4D">掌握提升领导力和执行力的8个解决方案</span></p><p style="margin-left:56px;line-height:150%"><span style=";line-height:150%;font-family:Wingdings;color:#4D4D4D">u<span style="font:9px &#39;Times New Roman&#39;">&nbsp; </span></span><span style=";line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;color:#4D4D4D">掌握提升领导力和执行力的具体方法和技巧；</span></p><p><strong><span style="font-size:7px;font-family:宋体;color:#4D4D4D">&nbsp;</span></strong></p><p style="margin-left:28px;line-height:150%"><span style=";line-height:150%;font-family:Wingdings;color:#4D4D4D">q<span style="font:9px &#39;Times New Roman&#39;">&nbsp; </span></span><strong><span style=";line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;color:#4D4D4D">课程时间：</span></strong><span style=";line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;color:#4D4D4D">2</span><span style=";line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;color:#4D4D4D">天（14h），也可根据企业需求调整为其他时长</span></p><p><span style=";font-family:宋体">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></p><p style="margin-left:28px;line-height:150%"><span style=";line-height:150%;font-family:Wingdings;color:#4D4D4D">q<span style="font:9px &#39;Times New Roman&#39;">&nbsp; </span></span><strong><span style=";line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;color:#4D4D4D">培训大纲</span></strong></p><p style="margin-left:28px;line-height:150%"><strong><span style=";line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;color:#4D4D4D">一、企业面临的困境（1h）</span></strong></p><p style="text-indent:27px;line-height:150%"><span style="font-family:宋体;color:#4D4D4D">1</span><span style="font-family:宋体;color:#4D4D4D">、设置了标准和规范，却不能保证员工严格执行；</span></p><p style="text-indent:27px;line-height:150%"><span style="font-family:宋体;color:#4D4D4D">2</span><span style="font-family:宋体;color:#4D4D4D">、制订了考核和奖惩，却调动不了员工的积极性；</span></p><p style="text-indent:27px;line-height:150%"><span style="font-family:宋体;color:#4D4D4D">3</span><span style="font-family:宋体;color:#4D4D4D">、员工各有各的小九九，团队总是无法同心同德；</span></p><p style="text-indent:27px;line-height:150%"><span style="font-family:宋体;color:#4D4D4D">4</span><span style="font-family:宋体;color:#4D4D4D">、管的松了人浮于事，管的严了阴奉阳违；</span></p><p style="text-indent:22px;line-height:150%"><strong><span style=";line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;color:#4D4D4D">【辅助工具】：本篇包括1段“精彩视频”和4个“经典案例”</span></strong></p><p style="text-indent:27px;line-height:150%"><span style="font-family:宋体;color:#4D4D4D">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="margin-left:28px;line-height:150%"><strong><span style=";line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;color:#4D4D4D">二、提升领导力和执行力的最佳解决途径(2h)</span></strong></p><p style="margin-left:28px;line-height:150%"><span style=";line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;color:#4D4D4D">1</span><span style=";line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;color:#4D4D4D">、企业管理实践经历的5个阶段</span></p><p style="margin-left:28px;line-height:150%"><span style=";line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;color:#4D4D4D">2</span><span style=";line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;color:#4D4D4D">、人本管理时代的两个管理环</span></p><p style="margin-left:28px;line-height:150%"><span style=";line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;color:#4D4D4D">3</span><span style=";line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;color:#4D4D4D">、领导力的5个层面</span></p><p style="margin-left:28px;line-height:150%"><span style=";line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;color:#4D4D4D">4</span><span style=";line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;color:#4D4D4D">、创造高效领导力和高效执行力的管理环境</span></p><p style="text-indent:22px;line-height:150%"><strong><span style=";line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;color:#4D4D4D">【辅助工具】：本篇包括1段“精彩视频”和8个“经典案例”</span></strong></p><p style="margin-left:28px;line-height:150%"><span style=";line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;color:#4D4D4D">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="margin-left:28px;line-height:150%"><strong><span style=";line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;color:#4D4D4D">三、提升领导力和执行力的8个引擎(11h)</span></strong></p><p style="margin-left:28px;line-height:150%"><strong><span style=";line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;color:#4D4D4D">1</span></strong><strong><span style=";line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;color:#4D4D4D">、第一个引擎——创造团队梦想(1h)</span></strong></p><p style="margin-left:56px;line-height:150%"><span style=";line-height:150%;font-family:Wingdings;color:#4D4D4D">ü<span style="font:9px &#39;Times New Roman&#39;">&nbsp; </span></span><span style=";line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;color:#4D4D4D">人类因梦想而发展</span></p><p style="margin-left:56px;line-height:150%"><span style=";line-height:150%;font-family:Wingdings;color:#4D4D4D">ü<span style="font:9px &#39;Times New Roman&#39;">&nbsp; </span></span><span style=";line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;color:#4D4D4D">主管都应成为”造梦师”</span></p><p style="margin-left:56px;line-height:150%"><span style=";line-height:150%;font-family:Wingdings;color:#4D4D4D">ü<span style="font:9px &#39;Times New Roman&#39;">&nbsp; </span></span><span style=";line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;color:#4D4D4D">团队愿景:员工的方向和动力源</span></p><p style="margin-left:56px;line-height:150%"><span style=";line-height:150%;font-family:Wingdings;color:#4D4D4D">ü<span style="font:9px &#39;Times New Roman&#39;">&nbsp; </span></span><span style=";line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;color:#4D4D4D">建立团队愿景的流程和方法</span></p><p style="margin-left:28px;line-height:150%"><strong><span style=";line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;color:#4D4D4D">2</span></strong><strong><span style=";line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;color:#4D4D4D">、第二个引擎——发现工作价值(1h)</span></strong></p><p style="margin-left:56px;line-height:150%"><span style="font-family:Wingdings">ü<span style="font:9px &#39;Times New Roman&#39;">&nbsp; </span></span><span style="font-family:宋体">发现工作的价值</span></p><p style="margin-left:56px;line-height:150%"><span style="font-family:Wingdings">ü<span style="font:9px &#39;Times New Roman&#39;">&nbsp;</span></span><span style="font-family:宋体">“卑微”中也蕴藏着伟大</span></p><p style="margin-left:56px;line-height:150%"><span style="font-family:Wingdings">ü<span style="font:9px &#39;Times New Roman&#39;">&nbsp; </span></span><span style="font-family:宋体">发掘工作价值的方法与技巧</span><strong><span style="text-underline:dottedtext-decoration:underline;"></span></strong></p><p style="margin-left:28px;text-indent:0;line-height:150%"><strong>3、</strong><strong><span style="font-family:宋体">第三个引擎——维护团队价值观（</span></strong><strong><span style=";line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;color:#4D4D4D">1h</span></strong><strong><span style="font-family:宋体">）</span></strong></p><p style="margin-left:56px;line-height:150%"><span style="font-family:Wingdings">ü<span style="font:9px &#39;Times New Roman&#39;">&nbsp; </span></span><span style="font-family:宋体">个人利益还是团队利益</span></p><p style="margin-left:56px;line-height:150%"><span style="font-family:Wingdings">ü<span style="font:9px &#39;Times New Roman&#39;">&nbsp;</span></span><span style="font-family:宋体">不要总看记分牌</span></p><p style="margin-left:56px;line-height:150%"><span style="font-family:Wingdings">ü<span style="font:9px &#39;Times New Roman&#39;">&nbsp;</span></span><span style="font-family:宋体">奖优不能罚劣</span></p><p style="margin-left:56px;line-height:150%"><span style="font-family:Wingdings">ü<span style="font:9px &#39;Times New Roman&#39;">&nbsp;</span></span><span style="font-family:宋体">清楚价值观不一致的队员</span></p><p style="margin-left:28px;line-height:150%"><strong><span style=";line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;color:#4D4D4D">4</span></strong><strong><span style=";line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;color:#4D4D4D">、第四个引擎——让工作成为快乐本源(1h)</span></strong></p><p style="margin-left:56px;line-height:150%"><span style="font-family:Wingdings">ü<span style="font:9px &#39;Times New Roman&#39;">&nbsp; </span></span><span style="font-family:宋体">快乐来源于工作成就</span></p><p style="margin-left:56px;line-height:150%"><span style="font-family:Wingdings">ü<span style="font:9px &#39;Times New Roman&#39;">&nbsp; </span></span><span style="font-family:宋体">“嗑瓜子”磕出的管理启示</span></p><p style="margin-left:56px;line-height:150%"><span style="font-family:Wingdings">ü<span style="font:9px &#39;Times New Roman&#39;">&nbsp; </span></span><span style="font-family:宋体">小成就让工作欲罢不能</span></p><p style="margin-left:56px;line-height:150%"><span style="font-family:Wingdings">ü<span style="font:9px &#39;Times New Roman&#39;">&nbsp; </span></span><span style="font-family:宋体">快乐工作的几个活力机制</span></p><p style="margin-left:28px;line-height:150%"><strong><span style=";line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;color:#4D4D4D">5</span></strong><strong><span style=";line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;color:#4D4D4D">、第五个引擎——让员工成为团队主角(2h)</span></strong></p><p style="margin-left:52px;line-height:150%"><span style="font-family:Wingdings">ü<span style="font:9px &#39;Times New Roman&#39;">&nbsp; </span></span><span style="font-family:宋体">领导要学会善其下</span></p><p style="margin-left:52px;line-height:150%"><span style="font-family:Wingdings">ü<span style="font:9px &#39;Times New Roman&#39;">&nbsp; </span></span><span style="font-family:宋体">让员工自定目标</span></p><p style="margin-left:52px;line-height:150%"><span style="font-family:Wingdings">ü<span style="font:9px &#39;Times New Roman&#39;">&nbsp; </span></span><span style="font-family:宋体">给员工创造四个舞台</span></p><p style="margin-left:52px;line-height:150%"><span style="font-family:Wingdings">ü<span style="font:9px &#39;Times New Roman&#39;">&nbsp; </span></span><span style="font-family:宋体">针对不同类型员工的授权法</span></p><p style="margin-left:28px;line-height:150%"><strong><span style=";line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;color:#4D4D4D">6</span></strong><strong><span style=";line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;color:#4D4D4D">、第六个引擎——做好员工的成长教练(2h)</span></strong></p><p style="margin-left:52px;line-height:150%"><span style="font-family:Wingdings">ü<span style="font:9px &#39;Times New Roman&#39;">&nbsp; </span></span><span style="font-family:宋体">员工成长需要时间和空间</span></p><p style="margin-left:52px;line-height:150%"><span style="font-family:Wingdings">ü<span style="font:9px &#39;Times New Roman&#39;">&nbsp; </span></span><span style="font-family:宋体">培育的关键：“补差”而非“普及”</span></p><p style="margin-left:52px;line-height:150%"><span style="font-family:Wingdings">ü<span style="font:9px &#39;Times New Roman&#39;">&nbsp; </span></span><span style="font-family:宋体">培育的</span>KASH<span style="font-family:宋体">模型</span></p><p style="margin-left:52px;line-height:150%"><span style="font-family:Wingdings">ü<span style="font:9px &#39;Times New Roman&#39;">&nbsp; </span></span><span style="font-family:宋体">实用教练步骤</span></p><p style="margin-left:52px;line-height:150%"><span style=";line-height:150%;font-family:Wingdings;color:#4D4D4D">ü<span style="font:9px &#39;Times New Roman&#39;">&nbsp; </span></span><span style="font-family:宋体">最有效的团队学习法</span></p><p style="margin-left:28px;line-height:150%"><strong><span style=";line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;color:#4D4D4D">7</span></strong><strong><span style=";line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;color:#4D4D4D">、第七个引擎——为成就相互喝彩(2h)</span></strong></p><p style="margin-left:56px;line-height:150%"><span style="font-family:Wingdings">ü<span style="font:9px &#39;Times New Roman&#39;">&nbsp; </span></span><span style="font-family:宋体">建立相互欣赏的团队环境</span></p><p style="margin-left:56px;line-height:150%"><span style="font-family:Wingdings">ü<span style="font:9px &#39;Times New Roman&#39;">&nbsp; </span></span><span style="font-family:宋体">真诚喝彩的“</span>TRUE<span style="font-family:宋体">”原则</span></p><p style="margin-left:56px;line-height:150%"><span style="font-family:Wingdings">ü<span style="font:9px &#39;Times New Roman&#39;">&nbsp; </span></span><span style="font-family:宋体">对过程的赞美比对结果赞美更重要</span></p><p style="margin-left:56px;line-height:150%"><span style="font-family:Wingdings">ü<span style="font:9px &#39;Times New Roman&#39;">&nbsp; </span></span><span style="font-family:宋体">高效表扬的四个技巧</span></p><p style="margin-left:56px;line-height:150%"><span style="font-family:Wingdings">ü<span style="font:9px &#39;Times New Roman&#39;">&nbsp; </span></span><span style="font-family:宋体">几种有效的非物质奖励法</span></p><p style="text-indent:28px;line-height:150%"><strong><span style=";line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;color:#4D4D4D">8</span></strong><strong><span style=";line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;color:#4D4D4D">、第八个引擎——创造高效沟通的团队氛围（1 h）</span></strong></p><p style="margin-left:56px;line-height:150%"><span style=";line-height:150%;font-family:Wingdings;color:#4D4D4D">ü<span style="font:9px &#39;Times New Roman&#39;">&nbsp; </span></span><span style=";line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;color:#4D4D4D">倾听，让人心凝聚起来</span></p><p style="margin-left:56px;line-height:150%"><span style=";line-height:150%;font-family:Wingdings;color:#4D4D4D">ü<span style="font:9px &#39;Times New Roman&#39;">&nbsp; </span></span><span style=";line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;color:#4D4D4D">学会积极正面的沟通反馈</span></p><p style="margin-left:56px;line-height:150%"><span style=";line-height:150%;font-family:Wingdings;color:#4D4D4D">ü<span style="font:9px &#39;Times New Roman&#39;">&nbsp; </span></span><span style=";line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;color:#4D4D4D">营造一个解决分歧的轻松氛围</span></p><p style="margin-left:56px;line-height:150%"><span style="font-size:12px;line-height:150%;font-family:Wingdings;color:#666666">ü<span style="font:9px &#39;Times New Roman&#39;">&nbsp; </span></span><span style=";line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;color:#4D4D4D">利用关系阶梯解决问题</span></p><p style="margin-left:28px;line-height:150%"><strong><span style=";line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;color:#4D4D4D">【辅助工具】：本篇包括4个“模拟体验”、8段“精彩视频”、22个“经典案例”和</span></strong></p><p style="text-indent:129px;line-height:150%"><strong><span style=";line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;color:#4D4D4D">16</span></strong><strong><span style=";line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;color:#4D4D4D">个实用的“管理技巧与工具”</span></strong></p><p style="margin-left:28px;line-height:150%"><span style=";line-height:150%;font-family:Wingdings;color:#4D4D4D">q<span style="font:9px &#39;Times New Roman&#39;">&nbsp; </span></span><strong><span style=";line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;color:#4D4D4D">课程特点：</span></strong></p><p style="margin-left:56px;line-height:150%"><span style=";line-height:150%;font-family:Wingdings;color:#4D4D4D">u<span style="font:9px &#39;Times New Roman&#39;">&nbsp; </span></span><strong><span style=";line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;color:#4D4D4D">视角独到：</span></strong><span style=";line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;color:#4D4D4D">讲师从多年的管理实践和企业培训中发现，影响领导力和执行力的根本因素是管理者过于依赖“事”为中心的职能管理，而忽视了以“人”为核心的团队管理。讲师认为创造高效执行的管理环境是团队领导力的最高境界，同是也是团队管理者最容易学习复制的领导力提升法。</span></p><p style="margin-left:56px;line-height:150%"><span style=";line-height:150%;font-family:Wingdings">u<span style="font:9px &#39;Times New Roman&#39;">&nbsp; </span></span><strong><span style=";line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;color:#4D4D4D">体验感强：</span></strong><span style=";line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;color:#4D4D4D">通过体验、视频、案例、研讨等方式将学员回归工作现场，冲击学员内心，引发学员反省，启动学员自我改变的引擎，从“要我变”，升华到“我要变”；</span></p><p style=";margin-left:56px;margin-bottom:0;line-height:150%;text-autospace:none"><span style=";line-height:150%;font-family:Wingdings;color:#4D4D4D">u<span style="font:9px &#39;Times New Roman&#39;">&nbsp; </span></span><strong><span style=";line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;color:#4D4D4D">实用性强：</span></strong><span style=";line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;color:#4D4D4D">不探讨繁冗的理论，重点剖析实际工作中的问题，提供科学实用的思路、流程、方法和工具，并针对核心环节进行现场训练，让学员从“知道”升华为“做到”；</span></p><p style=";margin-left:56px;margin-bottom:0;line-height:150%;text-autospace:none"><span style=";line-height:150%;font-family:Wingdings;color:#4D4D4D">u<span style="font:9px &#39;Times New Roman&#39;">&nbsp; </span></span><strong><span style=";line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;color:#4D4D4D">转化度高：</span></strong><span style=";line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;color:#4D4D4D">每个模块最后培训师都会指导学员设定训后的行动计划，保证培训效果的转移（将培训成果转为管理人员日常行为）</span></p><p style=";margin-left:56px;margin-bottom:0;line-height:150%;text-autospace:none"><strong><span style=";line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;color:#4D4D4D">&nbsp;</span></strong></p><p style="margin-left:28px;line-height:150%"><span style=";line-height:150%;font-family:Wingdings">q<span style="font:9px &#39;Times New Roman&#39;">&nbsp; </span></span><strong><span style=";line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;color:#4D4D4D">培训形式：</span></strong><span style=";line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;color:#4D4D4D">团队活动、模拟体验、案例研究、视频观摩、行为测试、专家授课等</span></p><p><br/></p>', 1374989498, 1),
(8, '通用管理', '《团队高效协作与执行管理模式》', '/upload/20130815/13765411668243.jpg', '王大泓、杨帆', '<p style="text-align:center;line-height:300%"><strong><span style="font-size:19px;line-height:300%;font-family:宋体;color:#333333">导入“全员、全方位、全过程”卓越团队管理模式</span></strong><br/></p><p style="text-align:right;line-height:150%"><strong><span style="font-size:16px;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;color:#333333">&nbsp;</span></strong></p><p style="line-height:150%;background:#F3F3F3"><strong><span style="font-size:19px;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;color:#333333">课程背景</span></strong></p><ul style="list-style-type: disc; " class=" list-paddingleft-2"><li><p style="line-height:150%"><span style="font-size:16px;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;color:#333333">有明确目标却无法保障实现；</span></p></li><li><p style="line-height:150%"><span style="font-size:16px;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;color:#333333">有规范流程却无法保障执行；</span></p></li><li><p style="line-height:150%"><span style="font-size:16px;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;color:#333333">有严密考核却无法驱动绩效；</span></p></li><li><p style="line-height:150%"><span style="font-family:宋体;color:#333333">…………….</span></p></li></ul><p style="text-indent:32px;line-height:150%"><span style="font-size:16px;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;color:#333333">这一系列的问题困扰着每一个管理者，有没有一种管理模式，可以激活团队和组织，使员工能够创造性工作，而不是被动完成任务；使员工能够主动超越目标，而不是应付考核；《团队高效协作与执行管理模式》从组织、文化、人性层面对企业管理过程中面临的实际问题进行深刻剖析，实现“全员、全方位、全过程”的高效能团队管理模式，推动企业管理升级。</span></p><p style="line-height:150%;background:#F3F3F3"><strong><span style="font-size:19px;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;color:#333333">课程受益</span></strong></p><ul style="list-style-type: disc; " class=" list-paddingleft-2"><li><p style="line-height:150%"><span style="font-size:16px;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;color:#333333">找到团队协作与执行不力的深层次原因</span></p></li><li><p style="line-height:150%"><span style="font-size:16px;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;color:#333333">找到提升团队协作与执行力的切入点</span></p></li><li><p style="line-height:150%"><span style="font-size:16px;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;color:#333333">掌握团队协作与执行力提升的“方法论”</span></p></li><li><p style="line-height:150%"><span style="font-size:16px;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;color:#333333">导入“全员、全方位、全过程”的卓越团队管理模式</span></p></li></ul><p style="line-height:150%;background:#F3F3F3"><strong><span style="font-size:19px;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;color:#333333">课程纲要</span></strong></p><p style="line-height:150%"><strong><span style="font-size:16px;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;color:#333333">&nbsp;</span></strong></p><p style="line-height:150%"><strong><span style="font-size:16px;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;color:#333333">第一单元：团队的协作与执行瓶颈</span></strong></p><p style="text-indent:187px;line-height:150%"><strong><span style="font-size:16px;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;color:#333333">——找到问题比解决问题更重要</span></strong></p><p style="margin-left:28px;text-indent:8px;line-height:150%"><span style="font-size:16px;line-height:150%;font-family:Wingdings;color:#333333">l</span><span style="font-size:16px;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;color:#333333">来自团队协作与执行无力的困扰</span></p><p style="margin-left:28px;text-indent:8px;line-height:150%"><span style="font-size:16px;line-height:150%;font-family:Wingdings;color:#333333">l</span><span style="font-size:16px;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;color:#333333">导致团队协作与执行无力的三个基本问题</span></p><p style="margin-left:28px;text-indent:8px;line-height:150%"><span style="font-size:16px;line-height:150%;font-family:Wingdings;color:#333333">l</span><span style="font-size:16px;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;color:#333333">制约团队协作与执行的三个障碍</span></p><p style="margin-left:28px;text-indent:8px;line-height:150%"><span style="font-size:16px;line-height:150%;font-family:Wingdings;color:#333333">l</span><span style="font-size:16px;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;color:#333333">团队高效协作与执行的三个决定要素</span></p><p style="margin-left:28px;text-indent:8px;line-height:150%"><span style="font-size:16px;line-height:150%;font-family:Wingdings;color:#333333">l</span><span style="font-size:16px;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;color:#333333">传统团队管理逻辑中的致命漏洞</span></p><p style="margin-left:28px;text-indent:8px;line-height:150%"><span style="font-size:16px;line-height:150%;font-family:Wingdings;color:#333333">l</span><span style="font-size:16px;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;color:#333333">快速提升团队协作与执行力的切入点</span></p><p style="line-height:150%"><strong><span style="font-size:16px;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;color:#333333">&nbsp;</span></strong></p><p style="line-height:150%"><strong><span style="font-size:16px;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;color:#333333">第二单元：团队高效协作与执行能管理模式</span></strong></p><p style="text-indent:178px;line-height:150%"><strong><span style="font-size:16px;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;color:#333333">——高效能管理模式是管理哲学与方法论的升级</span></strong></p><p style="margin-left:28px;text-indent:8px;line-height:150%"><span style="font-size:16px;line-height:150%;font-family:Wingdings;color:#333333">l</span><span style="font-size:16px;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;color:#333333">实现团队高效协作与执行的管理模式</span></p><p style="margin-left:28px;text-indent:8px;line-height:150%"><span style="font-size:16px;line-height:150%;font-family:Wingdings;color:#333333">l</span><span style="font-size:16px;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;color:#333333">团队高效协作与执行模式的管理哲学与逻辑</span></p><p style="margin-left:28px;text-indent:8px;line-height:150%"><span style="font-size:16px;line-height:150%;font-family:Wingdings;color:#333333">l</span><span style="font-size:16px;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;color:#333333">团队高效协作与执行模式的管理思维与导向</span></p><p style="margin-left:28px;text-indent:8px;line-height:150%"><span style="font-size:16px;line-height:150%;font-family:Wingdings;color:#333333">l</span><span style="font-size:16px;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;color:#333333">团队高效协作与执行模式的管理方法与对比</span></p><p style="margin-left:28px;text-indent:8px;line-height:150%"><span style="font-size:16px;line-height:150%;font-family:Wingdings;color:#333333">l</span><span style="font-size:16px;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;color:#333333">倍速提升团队协作与执行力的管理杠杆</span></p><p style="line-height:150%"><strong><span style="font-size:16px;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;color:#333333">&nbsp;</span></strong></p><p style="line-height:150%"><strong><span style="font-size:16px;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;color:#333333">第三单元：团队高效协作与执行模式的组织实践</span></strong></p><p style="text-indent:229px;line-height:150%"><strong><span style="font-size:16px;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;color:#333333">——管理动作不变，结果就不会改变</span></strong></p><p style="margin-left:28px;text-indent:8px;line-height:150%"><span style="font-size:16px;line-height:150%;font-family:Wingdings;color:#333333">l</span><span style="font-size:16px;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;color:#333333">团队高效能运作模式分析</span></p><p style="margin-left:28px;text-indent:8px;line-height:150%"><span style="font-size:16px;line-height:150%;font-family:Wingdings;color:#333333">l</span><span style="font-size:16px;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;color:#333333">团队成员的内在需求分析</span></p><p style="margin-left:28px;text-indent:8px;line-height:150%"><span style="font-size:16px;line-height:150%;font-family:Wingdings;color:#333333">l</span><span style="font-size:16px;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;color:#333333">团队与员工的双赢思考</span></p><p style="margin-left:28px;text-indent:8px;line-height:150%"><span style="font-size:16px;line-height:150%;font-family:Wingdings;color:#333333">l</span><span style="font-size:16px;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;color:#333333">团队成员的效能动力开发</span></p><p style="margin-left:28px;text-indent:8px;line-height:150%"><span style="font-size:16px;line-height:150%;font-family:Wingdings;color:#333333">l</span><span style="font-size:16px;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;color:#333333">基于人性与组织互动的团队管理实践</span></p><p style="margin-left:28px;text-indent:8px;line-height:150%"><span style="font-size:16px;line-height:150%;font-family:Wingdings;color:#333333">l</span><span style="font-size:16px;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;color:#333333">基于工作与组织文化溶合的团队管理实践</span></p><p style="line-height:150%"><strong><span style="font-size:16px;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;color:#333333">&nbsp;</span></strong></p><p style="line-height:150%"><strong><span style="font-size:16px;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;color:#333333">第四单元：团队高效协作与执行模式的系统化构建</span></strong></p><p style="text-indent:271px;line-height:150%"><strong><span style="font-size:16px;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;color:#333333">——卓越执行模式的系统化导入</span></strong></p><p style="margin-left:28px;text-indent:8px;line-height:150%"><span style="font-size:16px;line-height:150%;font-family:Wingdings;color:#333333">l</span><span style="font-size:16px;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;color:#333333">团队高效协作与执行力的环境保障与机制保障</span></p><p style="margin-left:28px;text-indent:8px;line-height:150%"><span style="font-size:16px;line-height:150%;font-family:Wingdings;color:#333333">l</span><span style="font-size:16px;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;color:#333333">团队高效协作与执行力的管理机制建设</span></p><p style="margin-left:28px;text-indent:8px;line-height:150%"><span style="font-size:16px;line-height:150%;font-family:Wingdings;color:#333333">l</span><span style="font-size:16px;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;color:#333333">团队高效协作与执行力的管理平台建设</span></p><p><br/></p>', 1374989712, 1);

